quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  16,1,"Ekiragiro kya Katonda kisembedde n'olwekyo temusaba kwanguwa kwakyo, (Katonda) yasukkuluma neyeesamba ku ebyo bye bamugattako"
  16,2,"Assa ba Malayika nga baleeta obubaka ku lw'ekiragirokye ku oyo gwaba ayagadde mu baddube, mutiise (abantu nga mubagamba nti), mazima tewali kisinzibwa kyonna (mu butuufu) okugyako nze kale nno muntye"
  16,3,"Yatonda eggulu omusanvu n'ensi lwa nsonga, musukkulumu nnyo ku ebyo bye bamugattako"
  16,4,"Yatonda omuntu nga amuggya mu mazzi agazaala, (bwakula) naafuuka omukaayanye ow'olwatu"
  16,5,"N’ebisolo ebirundibwa yabibatondera mufune mu byo okubuguma, n'emigaso (emirala) nga era kwe mulya"
  16,6,Era mulina mu byo okunyumirwa mu kiseera wemubiggyirayo ne mu kiseera wemubitwalirayo (ku ttale)
  16,7,"(Nga ebisolo ebimu) byetikka emigugu gya mmwe okugitwala eri ekitundu gye mutandituuse okugyako mu buzibu obw'ekitalo, mazima bulijjo Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe alumirwa nnyo wa kisa"
  16,8,"Era (yatonda) enfalaasi, n'e nyumbu n'endogoyi mube nga mubyebagala era nga bya kubasanyusa, era atonda ne bye mutamanyi"
  16,9,"Katonda y'alaga ekkubo ettuufu, ate amakubo agamu makyamu, singa yali ayagadde mwenna yandibalungamizza"
  16,10,"Yye yooyo abatonnyeseza enkuba okuva waggulu, ku nkuba eyo kwe munywa, era ku nkuba eyo emiti kwe gimerera nga ku gyo kwe muliisa ensolo za mmwe"
  16,11,"Abamereza nayo ebirimwa ne Zaituni n'emitende ne nzabibu nabuli bibala byonna, mazima mu ekyo mulimu akabonero (akalaga obuyinza) bwa Katonda eri abantu abafumiitiriza"
  16,12,Era yabagondeza ekiro n'emisana era enjuba n'omwezi n'emmunyeenye byonna byagonzebwa (bitambulira) ku kiragiro kye. Mazima mu ebyo byonna mulimu obubonero eri abantu abategeera
  16,13,"N’ebyo bye yabateera mu nsi nga amabala g'abyo tegafaanagana, mazima mu ekyo mulimu akabonero eri abantu abejjukanya"
  16,14,"Era yye, yooyo eyagonza enyanja mube nga mulya muyo ennyama (ebyenyanja) ebibisi era muggye mu yo eby'okwewunda bye mwambala. Ogenda noolaba amaato nga gakola ekkubo muyo, olwo nno musobole okugenda okunoonya ebigabwabye (Katonda), era kibasobozese okwebaza"
  16,15,"Era yassa mu nsi enkondo (ensozi) ereme kubayuuza, era nassaamu emigga, n'amakubo musobole okulungama"
  16,16,"Era naateeka (mu nsi) obubonero, okwo nno bwogattako emmunyeenye basobole okumanya gye balaga"
  16,17,Abange oyo atonda ayinza okuba nga atatonda! abaffe temujjukira
  16,18,"Ne bwe mubala ebyengera bya Katonda temusobola kubikomekkereza, mazima Katonda musonyiyi nnyo musaasizi"
  16,19,Era Katonda amanyi bye mukola mu kyama ne bye mukola mu lwatu
  16,20,Era abo bebasaba nebaleka Katonda tebatonda kintu kyonna ate nga bo batondebwa butondebwa
  16,21,(Bebasaba) bafu ssi balamu era tebamanyi ddi lwe balizuukizibwa
  16,22,"Katonda wa mmwe ali Katonda omu, abo abatakkiriza lunaku lwa nkomerero emitima gyabwe gikiwakanya era nga bo beekuza"
  16,23,"Tewali kubuusabuusa mazima Katonda amanyi bye bakweka ne bye bakola mu lwatu, era mazima yye tayagala beekuza"
  16,24,Bwe baba bagambiddwa nti Mukama omulabirizi wa mmwe kiki kyassizza bagamba nti nfumo za baasooka
  16,25,"Olwo nno balyoke beetikke ebibi bya bwe mu bujjuvu ku lunaku lw'enkomerero, era beetikke ne ku bibi bya abo be baabuza awatali kumanya, abange kibi kye beetikka"
  16,26,"Ab’abakulembera baakola enkwe, Katonda naasitula ebizimbe byabwe nga asinziira ku musingi akasolya nekabagwira waggulu waabwe ebibonerezo nebibajjira okuva webatasuubira"
  16,27,"Oluvanyuma ku lunaku lw'enkomerero agenda kubaswaza, era agambe nti baliwa bannange abo bemwayawukanangamu, baligamba abo abaaweebwa okumanya nti mazima obuswavu ne nnaku olwa leero bigenda kubeera ku bakaafiiri"
  16,28,Abo ba Malayika bebatuusa ku ntuuko zaabwe nga bakyeyisa bubi olwo nno nebalangirira okukkiriza Katonda (nga bwe bagamba nti) tetukolanga kibi kyonna. Nedda mazima Katonda amanyidde ddala ebyo bye mwakolanga
  16,29,Kale muyingire emiryango gyo muliro Jahannama mugenda kutuula mu gwo obugenderevu. Obuddo bwa beekuza bubi